00:22:14.640 --> 00:22:15.599
Well...

00:22:16.839 --> 00:22:18.799
The kid says he's made a decision.

00:22:22.000 --> 00:22:22.759
What?

00:22:23.640 --> 00:22:24.559
This...

00:22:25.799 --> 00:22:26.640
You tell us.

