What were you thinking, huh?

00:22:55.720 --> 00:22:57.359
Didn't you say before

00:22:58.279 --> 00:22:59.720
you wanted me to go to college?

00:23:00.400 --> 00:23:01.920
I never really figured out before

00:23:01.920 --> 00:23:03.759
what the point of me going to college was.

