You focus on your studies.

00:23:30.119 --> 00:23:32.799
Don't worry about your Third Uncle's business, okay?

00:23:36.799 --> 00:23:38.279
I've been researching all day today

00:23:39.119 --> 00:23:40.200
about Third Uncle's condition.

