Then don't think about this anymore.

00:23:55.839 --> 00:23:57.000
Just do your studying.

00:23:58.240 --> 00:23:58.839
Dad.

00:23:59.920 --> 00:24:01.279
You don't need to be anxious either.

00:24:02.480 --> 00:24:04.400
In the end, whether to have this surgery

00:24:05.160 --> 00:24:07.559
should be left for Third Uncle to decide himself.

00:24:54.839 --> 00:24:55.599
Come in.

00:24:58.319 --> 00:24:59.039
Doctor.

00:24:59.039 --> 00:25:01.400
Um, we're Ma Weiguo's family.

00:25:01.400 --> 00:25:02.880
Don't all come in at once.

00:25:02.880 --> 00:25:04.240
Just one person should come in.

00:25:05.680 --> 00:25:07.440
Right, okay, you all go out.

00:25:07.680 --> 00:25:08.440
Alright.

00:25:15.680 --> 00:25:16.279
Doctor.

00:25:16.279 --> 00:25:16.960
Please, have a seat.

00:25:26.119 --> 00:25:28.640
What's Ma Weiguo's current condition?

00:25:29.400 --> 00:25:30.799
The situation isn't very optimistic.

00:25:31.000 --> 00:25:32.039
As for surgery,

00:25:32.039 --> 00:25:33.200
the risk would be very high.

00:25:33.839 --> 00:25:35.160
If we go with conservative treatment,

00:25:35.319 --> 00:25:36.680
three to six months.

00:25:54.480 --> 00:25:55.279
Thanks.

