No.

00:26:09.119 --> 00:26:11.920
The doctor saw my phone when I went in, so I couldn't record.

00:26:12.119 --> 00:26:14.400
You should've just kept it in your pocket and recorded secretly. You...

00:26:14.400 --> 00:26:15.119
Exactly.

00:26:15.119 --> 00:26:15.839
Alright, here's the plan.

00:26:15.839 --> 00:26:19.039
Let's first get Weiguo discharged from the hospital.

00:26:26.559 --> 00:26:27.319
Let's go.

00:26:29.200 --> 00:26:29.759
Go.

00:26:31.160 --> 00:26:31.720
Go.

00:26:39.799 --> 00:26:40.920
No, no, no.

00:26:40.920 --> 00:26:41.880
You all go back.

00:26:41.880 --> 00:26:42.640
Get in bed and rest.

00:26:42.640 --> 00:26:43.359
Lie down for a bit, just lie down.

00:26:43.359 --> 00:26:43.920
The room is so small.

00:26:43.920 --> 00:26:44.799
What are so many people doing here?

00:26:44.799 --> 00:26:45.519
Come on, come on.

00:26:46.079 --> 00:26:46.759
No need.

00:26:46.880 --> 00:26:47.440
Lie down.

00:26:47.440 --> 00:26:48.079
Take off your shoes.

00:26:49.079 --> 00:26:50.200
Alright, alright, alright.

00:26:50.200 --> 00:26:51.160
Go back, go back, go back.

00:26:51.279 --> 00:26:52.000
Big Bro.

00:26:53.079 --> 00:26:54.640
Stop hovering around me, okay?

00:26:54.640 --> 00:26:55.920
Go do whatever you need to do.

00:26:55.920 --> 00:26:56.400
Alright.

00:26:56.400 --> 00:26:57.680
Aren't you all usually very busy?

00:26:57.680 --> 00:26:58.359
Not busy.

