Didn't I just...

00:28:10.920 --> 00:28:11.480
I said...

00:28:11.480 --> 00:28:13.920
The doctor said his physical condition is quite good now.

00:28:13.920 --> 00:28:14.599
Right?

00:28:14.720 --> 00:28:15.480
Really?

