No, look at you.

00:28:19.200 --> 00:28:21.000
You're about to be a father.

00:28:21.000 --> 00:28:22.759
Don't be on the verge of tears all the time, okay?

00:28:22.759 --> 00:28:23.720
I'm not, really.

00:28:24.920 --> 00:28:26.200
I'll talk to him later.

00:28:26.200 --> 00:28:27.279
I'll take you with me.

00:28:27.279 --> 00:28:28.319
Feel better now?

00:28:30.279 --> 00:28:30.960
Yeah.

00:28:31.319 --> 00:28:32.279
Alright, hurry up and go back.

00:28:32.279 --> 00:28:33.279
Go back, okay? I'm leaving.

00:28:33.279 --> 00:28:33.839
Okay.

00:28:33.839 --> 00:28:34.759
Then you...

