I'm actually quite lucky.

00:29:12.359 --> 00:29:13.920
What I have isn't the kind...

00:29:13.920 --> 00:29:15.720
...that leaves you bedridden, unable to do anything.

00:29:15.799 --> 00:29:17.680
Nor is it the kind where you drool when you talk...

00:29:17.680 --> 00:29:19.720
...and need help with every basic bodily function.

00:29:20.680 --> 00:29:22.160
If it really were like that...

00:29:22.920 --> 00:29:24.160
I'd rather kick the bucket sooner.

00:29:25.039 --> 00:29:26.039
Don't you worry.

00:29:26.039 --> 00:29:27.119
As for you...

00:29:27.480 --> 00:29:28.720
