Everyone's so busy.

00:30:04.799 --> 00:30:06.039
No matter how big a deal it is...

00:30:06.480 --> 00:30:08.119
...it won't be long before it's forgotten.

00:30:09.720 --> 00:30:11.680
Besides, Penglexuan is getting better and better.

00:30:11.720 --> 00:30:13.119
In the future, when we make a fortune...

00:30:13.119 --> 00:30:14.359
...eating, drinking, and having fun every day...

00:30:14.839 --> 00:30:15.960
...we'll be living even better lives.

00:30:16.599 --> 00:30:18.359
Who'll have time to worry about your problems?

00:30:31.519 --> 00:30:33.119
Hello? What's up?

00:30:33.920 --> 00:30:34.599
What?

00:30:35.119 --> 00:30:36.279
Yuanyuan still wants to emigrate.

00:30:36.640 --> 00:30:37.799
What nonsense is this?

00:30:38.160 --> 00:30:39.599
Wait there, I'm coming right over.

00:30:43.680 --> 00:30:44.480
Go ahead.

00:30:45.279 --> 00:30:46.839
I'm not dying anytime soon.

00:31:05.759 --> 00:31:07.279
I thought I had it figured out.

00:31:07.359 --> 00:31:08.240
But I don't.

00:31:09.119 --> 00:31:10.640
I thought they would understand me.

00:31:11.000 --> 00:31:11.759
They don't.

00:31:12.640 --> 00:31:13.960
I thought I understood them.

00:31:14.279 --> 00:31:15.279
I still don't.

00:31:16.799 --> 00:31:17.599
And also...

00:31:18.160 --> 00:31:19.599
...what counts as living in misery?

00:31:20.079 --> 00:31:21.640
What counts as dying meaningfully?

00:31:22.200 --> 00:31:23.680
Have I really figured it out?

00:31:33.000 --> 00:31:33.759
Mr. Chen

00:31:34.279 --> 00:31:35.640
I don't know why

00:31:35.759 --> 00:31:37.519
but you seem very familiar to me.

00:31:38.960 --> 00:31:40.160
Xiao Tong, right?

00:31:40.160 --> 00:31:41.640
You're quite good at breaking the ice.

00:31:42.599 --> 00:31:44.039
Tens of millions of years ago,

00:31:44.039 --> 00:31:45.400
we were all relatives.

00:31:47.279 --> 00:31:48.160
Well,

00:31:48.160 --> 00:31:50.920
I worked at my previous bank for fourteen years.

00:31:51.039 --> 00:31:52.720
I'm familiar with all the operations,

00:31:52.720 --> 00:31:54.680
and I've built up a solid client base.

00:31:56.359 --> 00:31:59.519
Since you were so stable at your last job,

00:31:59.960 --> 00:32:01.519
why the sudden desire to leave?

00:32:01.720 --> 00:32:02.519
I've been there too long.

00:32:02.519 --> 00:32:03.720
I just wanted a change of scenery.

00:32:03.720 --> 00:32:04.960
And I came here seeking

00:32:04.960 --> 00:32:06.519
greater opportunities for growth.

00:32:07.039 --> 00:32:08.039
I see.

00:32:09.519 --> 00:32:10.319
I'm sorry,

00:32:10.319 --> 00:32:13.640
but we currently have no openings at your level.

00:32:14.319 --> 00:32:15.279
That's okay.

00:32:15.279 --> 00:32:17.359
I can start from an entry-level position.

00:32:18.839 --> 00:32:20.319
After the background check results come in,

00:32:20.319 --> 00:32:21.519
we'll contact you again.

00:32:24.359 --> 00:32:26.400
A background check is mandatory?

00:32:26.720 --> 00:32:28.319
It's a required procedure.

00:32:28.599 --> 00:32:29.720
Is there a problem?

00:32:29.759 --> 00:32:31.279
No, no, no.

00:32:35.759 --> 00:32:36.680
Thank you.

00:32:43.839 --> 00:32:45.839
Yuanyuan said herself last time she didn't want to emigrate.

00:32:45.839 --> 00:32:47.000
She wanted to spend more time with me.

00:32:47.400 --> 00:32:49.079
Didn't Kevin hear it too?

00:32:49.079 --> 00:32:50.079
You think Yuanyuan is like you?

00:32:50.079 --> 00:32:51.160
Changing your mind on a whim?

00:32:51.400 --> 00:32:53.079
Why are you shouting so loud?

00:32:53.640 --> 00:32:55.640
I need you to keep your emotions in check, okay?

00:32:56.000 --> 00:32:57.480
You're scaring my daughter.

00:32:58.839 --> 00:32:59.720
Jenny.

00:33:00.440 --> 00:33:01.759
Tell Daddy yourself.

00:33:05.519 --> 00:33:06.240
Yuanyuan.

00:33:06.640 --> 00:33:07.400
Daddy's here.

00:33:07.400 --> 00:33:08.559
You don't need to be afraid.

